title: About
text:
Devin Alexander Nemetz-Simmons, born as Devin Alexander Simmons, is from Houston, Texas. Devin moved to San Diego, California, in 2006 and lived there for 11 years, then moved to The Woodlands, Texas, in 2017.
In his time at the University of Arizona, he spent his first year in Air Force ROTC and transferred to Army ROTC in his sophomore year. He received a Bachelor’s in History and a minor in military science upon his commission. He commissioned as a Field Artillery officer in the Texas National Guard. He is currently assigned to 1-133rd FA Regiment C-BATT. He started pursuing his master’s at The University of Texas at Dallas. He will attend FABOLC in March at Fort Sill, Oklahoma.

my_vars    <- c(income = "B19013_001", poverty = "B17001_002")
year_acs   <- 2023

# 4) Download

  geography = geo_level,
  variables = my_vars,
  state = state_abbr,
  year = year_acs,
  survey = survey,
  geometry = TRUE
)

Getting data from the 2019-2023 5-year ACS

# 5) Wide format
acs_wide <- acs |>
  tidyr::pivot_wider(
    id_cols = c(GEOID, NAME, geometry),
    names_from = variable,
    values_from = c(estimate, moe)
  )

# 6) Map
ggplot(acs_wide) +
  geom_sf(aes(fill = estimate_income), color = NA) +
  scale_fill_viridis_c(name = "Median HH Income") +
  labs(

  theme_minimal() +

    text = element_text(family = "Palatino"),
